## 00 — OVERVIEW

### Purpose of the Page

This document outlines the full content strategy, structure, and copy direction for Lady Adel's dedicated webpage within the IWC Concepts web application. It covers every section of the page — from the hero banner to the footer — with guidance on what to include, why it matters, and how it should be written.

The Lady Adel webpage will serve as her professional digital hub — a central destination that converts visitors from Catch Up With Lady Adel sessions into paying clients for training, consulting and coaching engagements. It must do four things simultaneously:

- **Establish credibility** — who Lady Adel is and why she is the right person to learn from
- **Showcase offerings** — training, consulting, Catch Up, speaking and the entrepreneur programme
- **Convert visitors** — get them to book, register or send an enquiry
- **Build community** — connect them to the broader IWC Concepts ecosystem

