## 02 — ABOUT LADY ADEL

> Where trust is built — the story behind the brand

This is where people decide whether they trust Lady Adel enough to invest their time or money. A biography that reads like a CV will lose people. The about section must read like a story — her journey, her transformation, and her mission.

### What Goes In

- **Short biography (story format)** — covering:
  - Her role as co-senior pastor at The HPC Global
  - Her banking background and years of corporate experience
  - Her EMBA in Corporate Finance and what it means practically for the people she serves
