  - Why she started IWC Concepts — to bridge the gap between spiritual purpose and professional success
  - Her identity as a Purpose-Profit Bridge
  - Who she serves and the transformation she creates in their lives

- **4 credibility highlight boxes** — displayed as icons with short text:

| Icon | Label |
|------|-------|
| 🏦 | Years of Corporate Banking Experience |
| 🎓 | EMBA — Corporate Finance |
| ⛪ | Co-Senior Pastor, The HPC Global |
| 🎙 | Host of Catch Up With Lady Adel |

