## 10 — RECOMMENDED PAGE FLOW

> The full visitor journey from top to bottom

Every section is ordered intentionally. The visitor is taken on a journey: first they are captured (Hero), then they trust (About), then they understand the offering (Services), then they are shown proof (Testimonials), and finally they take action (Contact). Do not reorder sections without careful consideration.

| Section | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| **HERO** | Who Lady Adel is + what she does + two CTAs. Must work in 5 seconds. |
| **ABOUT** | Her story, background and credibility highlights. Builds trust and connection. |
| **SERVICES** | Training / Bootcamp / Speaking / Coaching — specific offerings with CTAs. |
| **CATCH UP SPOTLIGHT** | Dedicated feature for the monthly programme with upcoming episode details. |
| **TESTIMONIALS** | Real voices from attendees and clients + impact counter numbers. |
| **MEDIA** | Podcast episodes, YouTube links and social media presence. |
| **ENTREPRENEUR PROGRAMME** | Full detail on the paid cohort programme with application CTA. |
| **CONTACT** | Simple form + WhatsApp button + email + response time commitment. |
| **FOOTER** | Logo, quick links, social icons, legal, copyright. |

